query:
SELECT g.id, g.nomeCompleto, c.id as consulta_id, c.alturaUterina, c.igUltrassomSemanas, c.igUltrassomDias, c.igDumSemanas, c.igDumDias, c.dataConsulta
FROM gestantes g 
JOIN consultasPrenatal c ON c.gestanteId = g.id 
WHERE g.nomeCompleto = 'TESTE TESTE'
ORDER BY c.dataConsulta;
